# Expo Router / RN

- Navigation themes/helpers: `expo-router/react-navigation`
- Bottom-tab helpers/types: `expo-router/js-tabs`
- Drawer layout: `expo-router/drawer`
- Alerts that must work on web: `utils/alert.ts` → `showAlert`
- Auth token storage and `/user/*` paths go through `services/authService.ts`
- Do not add cards/dashboard chrome to unfinished screens without an explicit design ask
